 2020-06412020-09-04,  PMO,  ,  , 
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule I.1 to that Act
PrecisOrder amending Schedule I.1 to the FINANCIAL ADMINISTRATION ACT by striking out the reference to the Deputy Prime Minister and Minister of Intergovernmental Affairs in column II of that Schedule opposite the name of the Canadian Intergovernmental Conference Secretariat in column I of that Schedule and by substituting for that reference a reference to the President of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada.
